  {
    "type": "message",
    "subtype": "thread_broadcast",
    "text": "As this thread started from search, I put together a short write up about the way we handle search in Glamorous Toolkit. <https://medium.com/feenk/pervasive-code-queries-in-the-ide-e0a23858e3a1>",
